        <scopecontent encodinganalog="520">
            <head>Scope and Content</head>
            <p>Files of correspondence containing more than 1,000 letters from Gallico and over 4,500 letters to Gallico from Harold Ober. There is also correspondence concerning Gallico. These files discuss literary works in progress, plans for future articles and books, contracts and financial agreements, and screenplays of his novels.</p>
            <p/>
        </scopecontent>
